summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit for the condemnation, appropriation, taking of certain real estate, as provided for in Ordinance No. 36755, being Cause No. 120973, insofar as the same affects certain property in blocks 19, 20, 22 and Marshall Reserve, in the First Plat of West Seattle by the West Seattle Land and Development Company, and in block 9, First Addition to First Plat of West Seattle Lane and Improvement Company, and in blocks 454 and 451, Seattle Tidelands; and appropriating money to pay all taxable costs incurred by the parties to said condemnation suit whose property is dismissed by this ordinance.
